    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't want to deal with the cost of a clinic visit for something that might just be a surface thing. if i use a thick layer of the manuka honey and wrap it tight with a sterile bandage, isn't that basically doing the same thing as a doctor closing it up? i feel like if i just keep it clean and let the honey do its thing, i'll be fine without needing any actual stitches or anything.",
